Pakistan Court Directs Zardari to Give Up Party Post, Dawn Says

-- B y   F a r h a n   S h a r i f
-- 
2011-05-13T05:01:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/pakistan-court-directs-zardari-to-give-up-party-post-dawn-says.html
A Pakistani court ordered President
Asif Ali Zardari to step down from his position as co-chairman
of the  Pakistan Peoples Party , Dawn newspaper  reported  citing
the court order.  The court ruled that holding of two offices is a violation
of the law, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Farhan Sharif in Karachi at 
 fsharif2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Naween Mangi at   nmangi1@bloomberg.net . 